              "id": "133f1156",
              "elType": "widget",
              "settings": {
                "html": "\n<!-- HERO -->\n<div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;min-height:100vh;background:#08122A;\">\n  <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:flex-end;padding:0 4rem 6rem 2.5rem;position:relative;z-index:2;background:#08122A;\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 80% at 20% 30%,rgba(196,154,42,0.06) 0%,transparent 60%);pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"position:relative;\">\n      \n      <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:1.8rem;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;flex-shrink:0;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;\">Our Story &amp; Mission</span></div>\n      <h1 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.8rem,5vw,5rem);font-weight:300;line-height:1.04;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 1.8rem;\">We exist because<br><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">800 million people</em><br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">deserve better.</strong></h1>\n      <p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.48);max-width:480px;margin:0;\">India's medtech innovation ecosystem is clustered in 5 cities and serves a fraction of the country. BMIIL was founded on a single conviction: that the next wave of healthcare breakthroughs won't come from a metro co-working space \u2014 they'll come from people who live with the problem every day.</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div style=\"position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#0F1F45;border-left:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.12);\">\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;top:50%;right:3rem;transform:translateY(-50%) rotate(90deg);transform-origin:center center;font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:9rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(196,154,42,0.18);white-space:nowrap;pointer-events:none;line-height:1;\">BMIIL</div>\n    <div style=\"position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:3rem;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(8,18,42,0.95) 60%,transparent);\">\n      <div style=\"width:32px;height:1px;background:#C49A2A;margin-bottom:1.2rem;\"></div>\n      <blockquote style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.35rem;font-weight:300;font-style:italic;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);line-height:1.65;max-width:420px;margin:0;\">\"The most important medical innovations of the next decade will be built by clinicians and engineers who understand what it means to live in <em style=\"color:#E2BF68;font-style:normal;\">Tier-2 India</em> \u2014 not just visit it.\"</blockquote>\n      <cite style=\"display:block;margin-top:1rem;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);font-style:normal;\">\u2014 BMIIL Founding Principle</cite>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- MISSION STRIP -->\n<div style=\"background:#C49A2A;padding:3rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 3px 1fr 3px 1fr;gap:2.5rem;align-items:center;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Incubate</h3><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.65);line-height:1.5;max-width:260px;margin:0 auto;\">Turn clinical insights and research into validated, fundable healthcare companies</p></div><div style=\"width:3px;height:60px;background:rgba(8,18,42,0.15);border-radius:2px;margin:0 auto;\"></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Validate</h3><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.65);line-height:1.5;max-width:260px;margin:0 auto;\">Give startups the clinical access, lab infrastructure, and regulatory expertise to prove their solutions work</p></div><div style=\"width:3px;height:60px;background:rgba(8,18,42,0.15);border-radius:2px;margin:0 auto;\"></div><div style=\"text-align:center;\"><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.3rem;\">Scale</h3><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.65);line-height:1.5;max-width:260px;margin:0 auto;\">Connect innovators to investors, hospital networks, and global markets \u2014 from Bareilly to the world</p></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- STORY + TIMELINE -->\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:7rem;align-items:start;\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Our Story</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.4rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 2rem;\">The gap that<br><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">demanded</em><br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">a response.</strong></h2>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.88;color:#4A5C78;\">\n        <p>Uttar Pradesh is home to over 240 million people \u2014 more than Brazil. It has one of the highest burdens of preventable disease in South Asia. And until BMIIL, it had <strong style=\"color:#08122A;font-weight:600;\">no dedicated medtech incubation infrastructure</strong> of any kind.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:1.3rem;\">The founding idea was simple and urgent: Bareilly International University already has the hospitals, the labs, the students, and the faculty. What it lacked was a structured system to convert clinical observations into startups.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin:2.5rem 0;padding:1.8rem 2rem;border-left:3px solid #C49A2A;background:#FFFFFF;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0;\">\n        <p style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.6;margin:0;\">\"Every day in a public hospital, doctors encounter problems that they know could be solved \u2014 if someone would just build the right tool. <em style=\"color:#C49A2A;font-style:normal;\">We are that someone.</em>\"</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.88;color:#4A5C78;\">\n        <p>BMIIL was built to be that bridge. Not a generic startup hub with a healthcare vertical \u2014 but a deeply clinical institution where the problem always comes before the product, and the patient always comes before the pitch.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:1.3rem;\">Situated within BIU's campus in Bareilly, we have direct access to a multi-speciality teaching hospital, specialised research laboratories, and a multidisciplinary faculty \u2014 giving our startups infrastructure that most metro incubators cannot offer at any price.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Journey So Far</p>\n      <div style=\"position:relative;\">\n        <div style=\"position:absolute;left:19px;top:8px;bottom:8px;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#C49A2A,rgba(196,154,42,0.1));pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;\">\n  <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#C49A2A;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">\u2713</span></div>\n  <div style=\"padding-top:0.6rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#C49A2A;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">2024 \u2014 Foundation</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">The Idea Takes Shape</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Dr. Varun Agarwal and Claudius Lazarus identify the gap in Tier-2 India's healthcare innovation infrastructure. Initial conversations with Bareilly International University begin.</p></div>\n</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;\">\n  <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#C49A2A;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">\u2713</span></div>\n  <div style=\"padding-top:0.6rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#C49A2A;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">2025 \u2014 Establishment</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">BMIIL is Founded</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Entity incorporated. Hosting agreement signed with BIU. First grant applications submitted. Core team begins forming around the founding vision.</p></div>\n</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;\">\n  <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#C49A2A;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;\">\u2713</span></div>\n  <div style=\"padding-top:0.6rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#C49A2A;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">2025\u201326 \u2014 Validation</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Institutional Backing Secured</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">First grant approvals received. Letters of intent signed with key partners. Mentor network assembled. Infrastructure setup underway on BIU campus.</p></div>\n</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;\">\n  <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#FFFFFF;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">\u2192</span></div>\n  <div style=\"padding-top:0.6rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#C49A2A;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">2026 \u2014 Launch</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Cohort 1 Opens</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">First cohort of 10\u201312 startups across Medtech Incubation, Accelerator, and Ayush tracks. Demo Day and first investor introductions planned for end of year.</p></div>\n</div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.5rem;padding-bottom:2.5rem;position:relative;\">\n  <div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:50%;background:#FFFFFF;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;position:relative;z-index:1;box-sizing:border-box;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;\">\u2192</span></div>\n  <div style=\"padding-top:0.6rem;\"><div style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:#C49A2A;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">2027 \u2014 Scale</div><div style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Replication Begins</div><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.65;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Second cohort launches. Framework for replicating the BMIIL model with partner universities across North India.</p></div>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- BIU -->\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:7rem 0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;gap:6rem;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Our Institutional Home</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3.4rem);font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.1;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Bareilly International<br>University \u2014 <em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">more than</em><br><strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">a host campus.</strong></h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.82;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.48);margin:0 0 2.5rem;\">BIU isn't a landlord \u2014 it's a co-creator. The University's clinical infrastructure, research faculty, and student talent pool are actively integrated into BMIIL's program delivery.</p>\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.1rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:38px;height:38px;min-width:38px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83c\udfe5</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Multi-Speciality Teaching Hospital</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);margin:0;\">1,200+ bed hospital with OPD, IPD, and surgical facilities \u2014 directly accessible to BMIIL startups for problem identification and pilot testing.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.1rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:38px;height:38px;min-width:38px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\u2697\ufe0f</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">12+ Specialised Research Labs</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);margin:0;\">Pharmacy, biotech, clinical pathology, dental, and allied health science labs \u2014 available for R&D, prototype testing, and formulation development.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.1rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:38px;height:38px;min-width:38px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83d\udc69\u200d\ud83d\udd2c</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">600+ Research Faculty</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);margin:0;\">Over 600 multidisciplinary academics across Medicine, Ayurveda, Pharmacy, Nursing, Dental, and Allied Health \u2014 available as subject matter experts and mentors.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.1rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:38px;height:38px;min-width:38px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83c\udf93</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Talent Pipeline</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.38);margin:0;\">Thousands of students across health science disciplines \u2014 a direct pool of future co-founders, clinical advisors, and early team members.</p></div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;margin:0 0 1.2rem;\">Constituent Colleges</p>\n      <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;\">\n        <a href=\"https://rmcbareilly.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\u2695\ufe0f</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">RMCH</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Rohilkhand Medical College & Hospital</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">MBBS, MD, MS \u2014 multi-speciality teaching hospital</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://ramch.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83c\udf3f</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">RAMCH</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Rohilkhand Ayurvedic Medical College & Hospital</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">BAMS \u2014 traditional medicine with modern research</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://www.idsbareilly.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83e\uddb7</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">IDS</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Institute of Dental Sciences</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">BDS \u2014 clinical and research dental facilities</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/rohilkhand-college-of-nursing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83e\ude7a</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">RCN</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Rohilkhand College of Nursing</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">B.Sc Nursing \u2014 clinical training & patient care</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/rohilkhand-college-of-nursing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83c\udfeb</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">RSN</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Rohilkhand School of Nursing</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">GNM \u2014 foundation nursing programme</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/rohilkhand-college-of-pharmacy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udc8a</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">RCOP</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Rohilkhand College of Pharmacy</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">B.Pharm, M.Pharm \u2014 drug discovery & formulation labs</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/biu-college-of-pharmacy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udd2c</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">BCOP</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">BIU College of Pharmacy</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">B.Pharm \u2014 pharmaceutical sciences & research</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://keshlatanursing.com/keshlata-college-of-pharmacy/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udc8a</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">KCOP</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Keshlata College of Pharmacy</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">B.Pharm \u2014 pharmacy education & practice</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/faculty-of-allied-and-health-care-sciences\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83c\udfc3</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">FAHS</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Faculty of Allied & Healthcare Sciences</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Physiotherapy, MLT, OT \u2014 diagnostics & therapy</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/faculty-forensic-sciences/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udd0d</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">FFS</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Faculty of Forensic Sciences</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Forensic science research & investigation</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://ffa.biu.edu.in/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83c\udfa8</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">FFA</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Faculty of Fine Arts</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Creative arts, design & visual communication</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/biu-college-of-humanities-journalism/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udcf0</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">BCHJ</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">BIU College of Humanities & Journalism</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Media, journalism & social sciences</p></div></a>\n        <a href=\"https://page.biu.edu.in/biu-college-of-management/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"text-decoration:none;display:block;\"><div style=\"background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);border-radius:3px;padding:1.3rem 1.2rem;transition:border-color .2s;\"><div style=\"font-size:1.2rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">\ud83d\udcbc</div><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;display:block;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">BCOM</span><h4 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">BIU College of Management</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;line-height:1.5;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">BBA, MBA \u2014 business & healthcare management</p></div></a>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:1.5rem;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:1.2rem;padding:1.2rem;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);border-radius:3px;\">\n        <div style=\"width:52px;height:52px;min-width:52px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid #C49A2A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#C49A2A;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);\"><img src=\"https://test.bmiil.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/05/logo-small.webp\" alt=\"BIU Logo\" style=\"width:48px;height:48px;object-fit:contain;display:block;border-radius:50%;\"></div>\n        <div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#FFFFFF;margin:0 0 0.15rem;\">Bareilly International University</h4><p style=\"font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">NAAC Accredited \u00b7 Pilibhit Bypass Road, Bareilly \u2014 243006</p></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- VALUES -->\n<div style=\"background:#EDE8DE;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align:center;max-width:580px;margin:0 auto 4rem;\">\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">What We Stand For</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.2rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.12;margin:0;\">The principles that<br>guide <em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">every</em> <strong style=\"font-weight:700;\">decision.</strong></h2>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.5rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">01</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Problem First, Always</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">We don't incubate technology \u2014 we incubate solutions to real clinical problems. Every startup that joins BMIIL must begin with a deeply understood, patient-validated problem statement. No exceptions.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">02</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Rigor Over Hype</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Healthcare is not a place for shortcuts. We demand clinical evidence, regulatory thinking, and intellectual honesty from every team we work with \u2014 and we model the same ourselves.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">03</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Tier-2 as a Strength</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">We don't apologise for being in Bareilly. We celebrate it. Lower costs, authentic problem exposure, and a healthcare market underserved for too long \u2014 this is an advantage, not a compromise.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">04</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Traditional Knowledge, Modern Evidence</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">India's Ayurvedic heritage is a globally unique innovation asset. We treat it with scientific seriousness \u2014 validating, protecting, and building on it rather than dismissing or romanticising it.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">05</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Founders Come First</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Our terms are founder-friendly. Our incentive is your success. We measure ourselves by the outcomes of our portfolio companies, not by the number of startups we admit.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.06);border-radius:4px;padding:2.2rem 2rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:3px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:4rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;opacity:0.12;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">06</span><h3 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.6rem;\">Build to Last</h3><p style=\"font-size:13px;line-height:1.75;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">We are not building a programme. We are building an institution \u2014 one designed to outlast any individual, any cohort, and any funding cycle.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- VISION -->\n<div style=\"background:#F7F3EC;padding:7rem 0;\">\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:7rem;align-items:center;\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">The Bigger Picture</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4vw,3.4rem);font-weight:300;color:#08122A;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 1.5rem;\">BMIIL isn't just<br>a centre \u2014 it's a<br><em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#C49A2A;\">replicable model.</em></h2>\n      <div style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.88;color:#4A5C78;\">\n        <p>India has 800+ universities outside its metro cities. The majority sit adjacent to district hospitals, have pharmacy and biotech facilities, and are surrounded by communities with unmet healthcare needs.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:1.2rem;\">BMIIL's Bareilly unit is designed to prove \u2014 rigorously and publicly \u2014 that a clinically-grounded medtech incubator can be built, funded, and sustained in Tier-2 India.</p>\n        <p style=\"margin-top:1.2rem;\">The long-term vision is a national network of BMIIL-model centres, each anchored to a university with clinical infrastructure, each generating a pipeline of locally relevant healthcare startups.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"margin-top:2.5rem;border:1px solid #EDE8DE;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;\">\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;background:#FFFFFF;\"><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;background:#08122A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;transform:rotate(180deg);letter-spacing:0.05em;\">2026</span></div><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Bareilly \u2014 Proof of Concept</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">First cohort. First validated startups. First exits or funding rounds.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;background:#FFFFFF;\"><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;background:#08122A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;transform:rotate(180deg);letter-spacing:0.05em;\">2027</span></div><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">North India Expansion</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">Two additional BMIIL centres in partner universities across UP and Uttarakhand.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;border-bottom:1px solid #EDE8DE;background:#FFFFFF;\"><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;background:#08122A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;transform:rotate(180deg);letter-spacing:0.05em;\">2028</span></div><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">National Medtech Network</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">A federated network of 5+ BMIIL-model centres contributing to a shared national deal flow.</p></div></div>\n        <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;background:#FFFFFF;\"><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;background:#08122A;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:1rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;writing-mode:vertical-rl;text-orientation:mixed;transform:rotate(180deg);letter-spacing:0.05em;\">2030</span></div><div style=\"padding:1.2rem 1.5rem;\"><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#08122A;margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Global Medtech Hub</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:#7A8BA8;margin:0;\">BMIIL-model centres contributing to India's position as a global medtech innovation hub.</p></div></div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1rem;\">\n      <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 1.8rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">800M+</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">underserved patients</span><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">In Tier-2 and Tier-3 India \u2014 the largest untapped healthcare market in the world.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 1.8rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">\u20b99L Cr</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">healthcare market</span><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">India's total healthcare market, majority concentrated in 8 metros today.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"grid-column:span 2;background:#C49A2A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 1.8rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#08122A;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">10\u201312</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.6);display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">startups per cohort</span><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(8,18,42,0.55);margin:0;\">Selected for depth of impact, clinical rigor, and team quality \u2014 not volume.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 1.8rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">incubation tracks</span><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Medtech, Accelerator, and Ayush \u2014 covering the full spectrum of healthcare innovation.</p></div>\n      <div style=\"background:#08122A;border-radius:4px;padding:2rem 1.8rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\"><div style=\"position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;background:#C49A2A;\"></div><span style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:2.8rem;font-weight:700;color:#C49A2A;line-height:1;display:block;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">12 months</span><span style=\"font-family:DM Mono;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);display:block;margin-bottom:0.5rem;\">programme duration</span><p style=\"font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;\">Structured phases from problem validation through regulatory readiness to investor introduction.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- CONTACT STRIP -->\n<div style=\"background:#08122A;padding:5rem 0;position:relative;overflow:hidden;\">\n  <div style=\"position:absolute;inset:0;background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(196,154,42,0.03) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:60px 60px;pointer-events:none;\"></div>\n  <div style=\"max-width:1220px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 2.5rem;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;position:relative;z-index:1;\">\n    <div>\n      <p style=\"display:inline-block;font-family:DM Mono;font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C49A2A;border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:2px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.1);margin:0 0 20px 0;\">Get in Touch</p>\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:Cormorant Garamond;font-size:clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem);font-weight:300;color:#FFFFFF;line-height:1.12;margin:0 0 1rem;\">Questions? Come<br>see us. <em style=\"font-style:italic;color:#E2BF68;\">We're here.</em></h2>\n      <p style=\"font-size:14px;line-height:1.75;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);margin:0 0 2rem;\">Whether you're a founder, investor, institution, or just curious \u2014 we welcome every conversation.</p>\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;\"><a href=\"/apply/\" style=\"background:#C49A2A;color:#08122A;font-weight:600;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:1px;padding:13px 28px;border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Apply Now \u2192</a><a href=\"https://test.bmiil.com/contact/\" style=\"background:transparent;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;padding:12px 24px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:2px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;\">Investor Enquiry</a></div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1.2rem;\">\n      <div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83d\udccd</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Address</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\">Bareilly International University<br>Pilibhit Bypass Road, Bareilly \u2014 243006<br>Uttar Pradesh, India</p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\u2709\ufe0f</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Email</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\"><a href=\"mailto:info@bmiil.com\" style=\"color:#C49A2A;text-decoration:none;\">info@bmiil.com</a></p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83c\udf10</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Website</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\"><a href=\"https://www.bmiil.com\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#C49A2A;text-decoration:none;\">www.bmiil.com</a></p></div></div><div style=\"display:flex;gap:1.2rem;align-items:flex-start;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;min-width:40px;border-radius:3px;background:rgba(196,154,42,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(196,154,42,0.25);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:1rem;\">\ud83c\udfdb\ufe0f</div><div><h4 style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);margin:0 0 0.2rem;\">Hosted By</h4><p style=\"font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);margin:0;line-height:1.6;\"><a href=\"https://biu.edu.in\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color:#C49A2A;text-decoration:none;\">Bareilly International University (BIU)</a></p></div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
